    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">凶会日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くゑにち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">凶会日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くゑにち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と見て<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">病</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">や</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>めるもの衰へしもの、<lb />
床の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にすなほに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">僵</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">瓶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の身は砕けてちりて、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">滅亡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほろび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に入らむ。<lb />
床の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">破</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れぬ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花瓶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はながめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
されどそが『こゝろ』は如何に、<lb />
すなほにと云へど、やさしき、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">砕</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くだ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>けにはあらず、はげしく<lb />
叫ぶを聞きぬ。<lb />
<lb />
人の子は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">瓶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にもあらず、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">運命</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うんめい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">運命</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うんめい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">観</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て、<lb />
秋のくれ、死ぬるといふ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
ほのかなる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">燭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">火</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のかげに、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">題目</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だいもく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をこそ――<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">蝋燭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ろうそく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はかすかに音し、<lb />
黄ばむ火は寒げに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">揺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れぬ。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">刻々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こく／＼</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">面</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がはりゆく<lb />
あゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死相</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しさう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>――<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">刹那</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せつな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ黒く、<lb />
つくは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">呻吟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うめき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">破瓶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">われがめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">画師</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">えし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>うち抱き、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しにびと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">法師</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほふし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みちびき、<lb />
秋の野へ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">葬</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">途</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
また聞きぬ、見ぬ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黒牛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くろうし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
これも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">呻吟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うめき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
